cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper proposes a Bayesian technique for segmentation and uncertainty quantification, which involves optimization and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions medical applications, which could fall under the sub-category of neural engineering (cs.NE). Finally, the paper uses synthetic and real images, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM).
